®In loving memory of
Roger Grenfell Toulson
23.09.1946 - 27.06.2017
Who loved these gardens and knew them well.
"A tree is known by its fruits and a man by his deeds""«
½In memory of Diana Cooper (1945-1994)
Deeply caring mother and family barrister
Sadly she left us too soon but she will always be loved by her children
Sarah and Julian"«
